---
title: Cal Smart Apple Turkey Stuffing Bowls with Sage Gravy
description: We all know everyone's favourite part of festive dinners is the stuffing, so why not have it for dinner? Our turkey, apple and squash stuffing bowl will have you longing to cozy up to a fireplace!

